entities.createSql: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`id` INTEGER NOT NULL, `url` TEXT NOT NULL, `name` TEXT NOT NULL, `artistName` TEXT NOT NULL, `bigImgUrl` TEXT NOT NULL, `smallImgUrl` TEXT NOT NULL, `albumName` TEXT NOT NULL, `date` INTEGER NOT NULL, `durationFormatted` TEXT NOT NULL, `durationInMillis` REAL NOT NULL, `ownerId` INTEGER NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY(`id`))

contentSyncTriggers: CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_fts_tracks_table_BEFORE_UPDATE BEFORE UPDATE ON `tracks_table` BEGIN DELETE FROM `fts_tracks_table` WHERE `docid`=OLD.`rowid`; END
CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_fts_tracks_table_BEFORE_DELETE BEFORE DELETE ON `tracks_table` BEGIN DELETE FROM `fts_tracks_table` WHERE `docid`=OLD.`rowid`; END

CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_fts_tracks_table_AFTER_UPDATE AFTER UPDATE ON `tracks_table` BEGIN INSERT INTO `fts_tracks_table`(`docid`, `name`, `artistName`, `ownerId`) VALUES (NEW.`rowid`, NEW.`name`, NEW.`artistName`, NEW.`ownerId`); END

CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_fts_tracks_table_AFTER_INSERT AFTER INSERT ON `tracks_table` BEGIN INSERT INTO `fts_tracks_table`(`docid`, `name`, `artistName`, `ownerId`) VALUES (NEW.`rowid`, NEW.`name`, NEW.`artistName`, NEW.`ownerId`); END
entities.createSql: CREATE VIRTUAL TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` USING FTS4(`name` TEXT NOT NULL, `artistName` TEXT NOT NULL, `ownerId` INTEGER NOT NULL, content=`tracks_table`)
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`queryTerm` TEXT NOT NULL, `time` INTEGER NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY(`queryTerm`))
